cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is about improving the efficiency of portrait segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a new architecture that reduces the number of parameters while maintaining good learning capacity, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, since the paper deals with image processing, it may also belong to the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
